n;\u0009Bradley Hyman;\u0009V,H,Perry;\u0009Ma'),NULL,'RNA-Seq of cortical and hippocampal microglia in female and male C57Bl/6 wild type mice and in AppNL-G-F mice M3, M6, M12, M21 (32 experimental conditions, 2 mice per condition - data pooled). ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,unistr('Name: Bart de Strooper;\u0009Email: bart.destrooper@kuleuven.be;\u0009Department: VIB-KU Leuven Center for Brain & Disease Research;\u0009Institute: KULeuven;\u0009Address: Campus Gasthuisberg, Herestraat 49, bus 602;\u0009City: Leuven;\u0009Zip/postal_code: 3000;\u0009Country: Belgium'),unistr('ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/series/GSE127nnn/GSE127892/suppl/GSE127892_microglia.kw.SeuratNorm.tsv.gz;\u0009ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/series/GSE127nnn/GSE127892/suppl/GSE127892_microglia.kw.meta.csv.gz;\u0009ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/series/GSE127nnn/GSE127892/suppl/GSE127892_microglia.kw.raw.tsv.gz'));
